### Code

```elixir
defmodule Parser do
  def parse(input) do
    input
    |> String.split("\n\n")
    |> Enum.map(fn val ->
      String.split(val, "\n")
      |> Enum.map(&String.to_integer(&1))
    end)
  end
end
```

