## Part One

### Code

```elixir
defmodule PartOne do
  def resolve(input) do
    IO.puts("--- Part One ---")
    IO.puts("Result: #{run(input)}")
  end

  def run(input) do
    input
    |> Parser.parse()
    |> Enum.map(&Enum.sum(&1))
    |> Enum.max()
  end
end
```

